  "title": "FINANCE & ADMIN EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a self-motivated Finance and HR Executive. You have the chance to be one of our core team to implement systems and procedures to corporatize our business<br /><br />Our business includes a retail segment with 2 retail chains selling fast moving consumer goods and religious products, a property rental segment and a direct selling segment<br /><br /><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br /><br />Accounting, General Admin Functions<br /></p><ul><li>Responsible for the full set accounts and day-to-day accounting</li><li>Perform bookkeeping general ledger, AP, cash management, and bank reconciliation</li><li>Ensure all accounting records are kept up-to-date and maintained promptly and accurately</li><li>Handle all regulatory submissions including GST returns</li><li>Process payments to suppliers</li><li>Liaise with the external auditor and tax agents</li><li>Report to the Directors and handle ad-hoc assignments</li><li>HR Functions</li></ul><p><br />Responsible for full spectrum of HR function<br /></p><ul><li>Responsible in payroll process, claims expenses, and other related matters</li><li>Manage recruitment cycle including sourcing, arrange for interview, and salary proposal</li><li>Process Work pass application, renewable and cancellation</li><li>Coordinate with insurance agents with regards to cancellation, renewal, new coverage of insurances</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>ACCA/Diploma in Accounting or equivalent with 2 years of relevant work experience</li><li>Possess knowledge in GST, Local Tax Regulations, and Singapore Financial Reporting Standards (FRS)</li><li>Self -motivated. well organized, meticulous, and able to multi-task</li></ul>",
